name: Tunnel of Cycles and Visions
description: This dimension is full of cycles, cycles of life, cycles of light, cycles of love. But what cycles lie beyond this dimension? When we have visions or induce them, the boundary between this dimension's cycles and the next get intertwined sometimes interweaved and often leave a message. We are just a cycle, there is no beginning and no end, just now.   Sound by Cosinus  2160X2160 1260frames@60FPS (0:21) - HIGHER DEFINTION VERSION (BETTER ENCODING) AVAILBLE TO BUYERS
